Bonsai GBA - A Lean, Optimized GBA Emulator for PSP
====================================================

Copyright (C) 2026 Bonsai GBA Project Contributors
Forked from FrogGBA, which is itself based on TempGBA4PSP and gameplaySP kai.

This software is a derivative work based on:
- gameplaySP kai by Exophase (2006) and takka (2007)
- TempGBA by Nebuleon, Normmatt, and BassAceGold
- TempGBA4PSP modifications by various contributors
- FrogGBA modifications and overlay system by the FrogGBA Project (2024)
- Bonsai GBA optimizations and modifications by the Bonsai GBA Project (2026)

